text:
I'm looking forward to seeing what kind
of stage Juri will show with this costume.
Though I don't really have a plan……

Oh, sorry,
I didn't mean to pressure you.

As long as Juri shines in her own way,
that's the best.
That's what puts the pressure on me!

Well, it's not something you can
figure out right away....
I wonder if the day will come when I understand……
Well, I won't rush it too much.
